### 6. **The Gazette Text Round-Trip (Split→Join→Split Sandwich)**

**File**: `/Users/bhyslop/projects/rbm_beta_recipemuster/Tools/jjk/vov_veiled/src/jjrz_gazette.rs`

**Parse (split) path** (lines 100-167):
